  </div>

  <div class="col-2">
    <p>I spent over a decade in executive leadership building teams and navigating organizational complexity. I know what works when you're leading through real challenges because I've done it, made the mistakes, learned what matters.</p>

    <p>I'm a Professional Certified Coach with the International Coaching Federation, with training in coaching methodologies that focus on adult development and how people actually change. I've designed and delivered leadership programs for organizations across different industries, working with hundreds of leaders at different levels and functions.</p>

    <p>These programs engage the whole person—cognitive understanding, emotional awareness, embodied practice. I trust that leaders have their own wisdom and my role is creating conditions where that wisdom can emerge and develop.</p>

